00:51:59,301 --> 00:52:03,667
Hei.

446
00:52:09,538 --> 00:52:13,178
Adakah anda gila?

447
00:52:13,178 --> 00:52:18,304
Anda mahu meletupkannya di mana-mana

448
00:52:18,304 --> 00:52:22,171
bahawa pemilik WR sedang nazak?

449
00:52:36,485 --> 00:52:37,863
Adakah anda juga berfikir?

450
00:52:37,863 --> 00:52:41,161
Saya minta maaf.

451
00:52:41,851 --> 00:52:45,686
Pengerusi.

452
00:52:45,686 --> 00:52:48,965
Awak tahu saya dah buat semua yang saya mampu untuk awak,

453
00:52:54,630 --> 00:52:57,261
kan?

454
00:52:58,980 --> 00:53:01,667
Apabila anda pergi...

455
00:53:19,507 --> 00:53:22,033
Pastikan bahagian Hee Jin adalah
jelas dijamin dalam kehendak anda.

456
00:53:24,620 --> 00:53:27,126
Ya?

457
00:53:37,465 --> 00:53:40,444
Awak...

458
00:53:43,043 --> 00:53:47,589
Ya?

459
00:54:04,071 --> 00:54:06,544
Apa sahaja yang anda tarik,

460
00:54:31,498 --> 00:54:32,519
tutupnya.

461
00:54:32,519 --> 00:54:37,525
Ya,

462
00:54:37,525 --> 00:54:39,372
Saya tidak tahu, anda telah bekerja sendiri

463
00:54:39,372 --> 00:54:41,236
hingga ke tulang seperti itu.

464
00:54:41,236 --> 00:54:43,519
Pengarah, ada apa-apa yang boleh saya bantu?

465
00:54:43,519 --> 00:54:48,338
Saya minta maaf.

466
00:54:49,404 --> 00:54:52,388
<i>Kita patut kuburkan rakaman itu.</i>

467
00:54:52,388 --> 00:54:55,448
Ya.

468
00:55:45,389 --> 00:55:48,036
Kami membunuh projek ini di sini.

469
00:55:56,081 --> 00:56:00,445
Tarik semua yang terikat
Park Jae Sang dan Oh Kwang Jae.

470
00:56:00,445 --> 00:56:02,758
Dan menangguhkan keluaran rakaman.

471
00:56:04,778 --> 00:56:08,105
<i>Faham.</i>

472
00:56:17,125 --> 00:56:21,872
Dengan pengerusi terlibat,
ia terlalu berisiko untuk terus menolak.

473
00:56:21,872 --> 00:56:24,165
Saya akan menghubungi Park Jae Sang
dan menangguhkan projek itu.

474
00:56:30,153 --> 00:56:32,627
Dan

475
00:56:35,472 --> 00:56:37,792
bawakan saya Pelan B.

476
00:56:55,633 --> 00:56:59,181
<i>Faham.</i>

477
00:56:59,181 --> 00:57:02,313
Alamak.

478
00:57:20,544 --> 00:57:22,963
Encik Park,

479
00:57:24,089 --> 00:57:28,133
kami membatalkan keluaran rakaman.

480
00:57:28,133 --> 00:57:31,516
<i>Apa?</i>

481
00:57:39,432 --> 00:57:43,945
<i>Adakah anda bergurau dengan saya sekarang?</i>

482
00:57:45,111 --> 00:57:48,004
Choi Ji Ho tidak bertemu Park Jae Sang hari ini.

483
00:57:51,358 --> 00:57:53,874
Nampaknya Lee Yang Mi telah menarik palamnya.

484
00:57:53,874 --> 00:57:56,464
<i>Mereka baru sahaja menutup rakaman,</i>

485
00:57:56,464 --> 00:58:00,184
<i>dan Park Jae Sang kedengaran marah.</i>

486
00:58:00,184 --> 00:58:03,428
<i>Saya akan kekal bersamanya.</i>

487
00:58:03,428 --> 00:58:05,691
Kenapa awak buat begini sekarang?

488
00:58:05,691 --> 00:58:06,716
<i>Ia adalah rumit. Kita jumpa nanti dan...</i>

489
00:58:06,716 --> 00:58:10,469
"Nanti?" Bilakah masanya nanti?

490
00:58:10,469 --> 00:58:15,075
Awaklah yang mengheret saya ke dalam perkara ini.

491
00:58:15,075 --> 00:58:16,869
Jika anda mahu keluar, anda keluar.

492
00:58:16,869 --> 00:58:19,866
Saya tidak akan membiarkan Chu Sang Ah pergi.

493
00:58:19,866 --> 00:58:22,332
Hei, Encik Park...

494
00:58:26,198 --> 00:58:28,558
Jangan buat apa-apa terburu-buru...

495
00:58:31,953 --> 00:58:34,620
Hei!

496
00:58:34,620 --> 00:58:37,670
Sial.

497
00:58:37,670 --> 00:58:39,950
<i>Nombor yang anda dail tidak tersedia.</i>

498
00:58:40,637 --> 00:58:44,013
Mengapa dia tidak mengangkatnya?

499
00:58:44,013 --> 00:58:47,710
Lintah.

500
00:58:47,710 --> 00:58:49,794
Apa...

501
00:58:49,794 --> 00:58:52,517
Ya ampun,

502
00:58:52,517 --> 00:58:55,197
seorang gadis manis membantu dengan ini...

503
00:58:55,197 --> 00:58:57,976
Bukan apa.

504
00:59:05,959 --> 00:59:07,949
Nah...

505
00:59:07,949 --> 00:59:11,006
Anda tidak mengenali saya?

506
00:59:11,006 --> 00:59:13,966
Saya rasa seperti

507
00:59:13,966 --> 00:59:17,739
saya pernah melihat awak di suatu tempat.

508
00:59:19,954 --> 00:59:22,994
Tentang Jae Sang... dari dulu...

509
00:59:23,861 --> 00:59:25,729
Kemudian awak...

510
00:59:25,729 --> 00:59:28,235
Chu Sang Ah?

511
00:59:29,521 --> 00:59:31,811
Saya minta maaf.

512
00:59:31,811 --> 00:59:33,328
Saya hanya terharu ketika itu.

513
00:59:33,328 --> 00:59:35,694
Saya tidak pernah terfikir ia akan berlaku.

514
00:59:36,467 --> 00:59:38,691
Sekali sahaja...

515
00:59:38,691 --> 00:59:42,284
Maafkan saya, tolong.

516
00:59:45,434 --> 00:59:47,887
- Saya minta maaf.
- Jangan lakukan ini.

517
00:59:49,726 --> 00:59:52,273
Tolong maafkan saya.

518
00:59:58,041 --> 00:59:59,380
Saya minta maaf.

519
00:59:59,380 --> 01:00:01,715
Saya minta maaf, puan. Saya tidak tahu ketika itu.

520
01:00:01,715 --> 01:00:04,018
Saya tidak tahu anda tidak boleh pergi begitu sahaja
selepas merosakkan hidup seseorang.

521
01:00:17,040 --> 01:00:19,146
Saya minta maaf.

522
01:00:20,540 --> 01:00:22,750
Tolong jangan lakukan ini.

523
01:00:22,750 --> 01:00:24,257
Tolong maafkan saya.

524
01:00:24,257 --> 01:00:27,824
Saya minta maaf.

525
01:00:27,824 --> 01:00:31,677
- Saya minta maaf.
- Sang Ah.

526
01:00:36,760 --> 01:00:38,877
Sudah lama,

527
01:00:38,877 --> 01:00:41,942
Park Jae Sang.

528
01:00:41,942 --> 01:00:44,449
<i>Awak bersama Sang Ah malam tadi, kan?</i>

529
01:00:45,061 --> 01:00:48,661
<i>Kenapa awak gelabah?</i>

530
01:00:50,349 --> 01:00:54,428
<i>Mari kita tamatkan ini.</i>

531
01:00:55,967 --> 01:00:57,897
<i>Saya tidak boleh menamatkannya seperti ini.

532
01:00:57,897 --> 01:01:01,104
<i>jika Chu Sang Ah turun,
begitu juga Pendakwaraya Bang.</i>

533
01:01:01,920 --> 01:01:04,327
<i>Saya akan menghalangnya,
walaupun saya perlu membunuh bajingan itu.

534
01:01:04,327 --> 01:01:07,319
Please forgive me.

535
01:01:07,319 --> 01:01:09,097
I'm sorry.

536
01:01:09,097 --> 01:01:13,346
I'm so sorry, ma'am. I didn't know back then.

537
01:01:13,346 --> 01:01:17,474
I didn't know you can't just walk away
after ruining someone's life.

538
01:01:17,474 --> 01:01:18,917
I'm sorry.

539
01:01:18,917 --> 01:01:22,345
Please don't do this.

540
01:01:22,345 --> 01:01:25,267
Please forgive me.

541
01:01:25,981 --> 01:01:29,007
I'm so sorry.

542
01:01:29,644 --> 01:01:32,442
- I'm sorry.
- Sang Ah.

543
01:01:48,923 --> 01:01:51,696
It's been a while,

544
01:01:55,335 --> 01:01:57,720
Park Jae Sang.

545
01:02:43,086 --> 01:02:46,037
<i>You were with Sang Ah last night, weren't you?</i>

546
01:02:46,037 --> 01:02:49,062
<i>Why are you so on edge?</i>

547
01:02:49,062 --> 01:02:51,518
<i>Let's end this.</i>

548
01:02:51,518 --> 01:02:53,247
<i>I can't end it like this.</i>

549
01:02:53,247 --> 01:02:54,716
<i>I'm going to expose everything.</i>

550
01:02:54,716 --> 01:02:55,957
<i>You know,</i>

551
01:02:55,957 --> 01:02:58,470
<i>if Chu Sang Ah goes down,
so does Prosecutor Bang.</i>

552
01:02:58,470 --> 01:03:00,927
<i>I'll stop him,
even if I have to kill the bastard.</i>

553
01:03:00,927 --> 01:03:04,114
<i>I'll take point on the tentpole.</i>

554
01:03:04,114 --> 01:03:07,107
<i>Make it bold</i>

555
01:03:07,107 --> 01:03:09,907
<i>and hit hard.</i>

